---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Aurais" description="AI assistant with integrated governance - Mission control for AI agents">
  <article class="py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <a href="/projects" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white mb-6">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
          </svg>
          Back to Projects
        </a>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-vorion-500/20 to-accent-cyan/20 border border-vorion-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl">
            ðŸ¤–
          </div>
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Aurais</h1>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/30 flex items-center gap-1">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                Live
              </span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium rounded-full bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/30">
                README Available
              </span>
              <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">Proprietary</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          AI assistant with integrated governance. Real-time monitoring, human-in-the-loop approval
          workflows, and mission control for your AI agent fleet.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-12 p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
        <a
          href="https://aurais.agentanchorai.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-vorion-500 hover:bg-vorion-600 text-white transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
          </svg>
          Open Aurais
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Notice -->
      <div class="mb-12 p-6 rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/30">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-amber-400 mb-1">Proprietary Application</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-amber-200/70">
              Aurais is a proprietary application. The Agent SDK used for connecting agents is open source.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Overview -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Aurais serves as the mission control interface for AI agent operations. Unlike traditional
          chatbots, Aurais maintains awareness of agent trust levels, enforces governance policies,
          and provides human operators with the tools to oversee autonomous operations.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Agents connect to Aurais via the open-source Agent SDK, enabling real-time status updates,
          task assignment, and approval request workflows.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Features -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Capabilities</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Agent Fleet View</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Real-time visibility into all connected agents. Monitor status, current tasks,
              and trust scores from a unified dashboard.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Task Assignment</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Assign tasks to agents based on capability and trust level. Automatic routing
              respects governance policies.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Approval Queues</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Review and approve high-risk agent actions. Severity-based routing ensures
              appropriate stakeholder review.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Chat Interface</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Natural language interaction with the AI system. Queries are processed
              through governance-aware routing.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- SDK -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Agent SDK</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">
          Connect your agents to Aurais using the open-source SDK:
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-800/50 border-b border-slate-700">
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-400">TypeScript</span>
          </div>
          <pre class="p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto"><code class="text-slate-300">import {'{'} AuraisAgent {'}'} from '@vorion/agent-sdk';

const agent = new AuraisAgent({'{'}
  apiKey: process.env.AURAIS_API_KEY,
  capabilities: ['execute', 'external'],
  skills: ['data-analysis', 'web-dev'],
{'}'});

agent.on('task:assigned', async (task) => {'{'}
  await agent.updateStatus('WORKING');
  // ... execute task
  await agent.completeTask(task.id, result);
{'}'});

await agent.connect();</code></pre>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Related -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Related</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/projects/agentanchor" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
            AgentAnchor
          </a>
          <a href="/packages#agent-sdk" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
            @vorion/agent-sdk
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
